kernels are launched with a configuration
execution config has number of blocks in a grid and number of threads per grid 
every block in the grid has same number of threads 
gridDim.x is the number of blocks in a grid 
blockDim.x is the number of threas in a block
blockIdx.x is the index of the current block in the grid 
threadIdx.x is the index of the current thread in the block. 
